text: For anyone looking to connect with Dell, Austin has some great information.

elements.text: For anyone looking to connect with Dell, Austin has some great information

Hey first years!  I interned at Dell last year, but my internship did not come from on campus recruiting.  I interned with Dell Technologies Services (DTS) which doesn't recruit on campus, but does recruit MBA and graduate level interns.  I was talking with some people in DTS HR and they sent me some QR codes for internships in DTS.  There are some business, analytics, and data science MBA/graduate level internships.  Scan the QR codes and apply if you are interested!
